book.title: Jared's Wolf (Wyndham Werewolf #2)
book.description: Storyline: Jared's Wolf (Wyndham Werewolf #2) \n Jared Rocke will do anything avenge his sister's death, even believe in werewolves. What he doesn?t believe is that he's attracted to Moira Wolfbauer, the she-wolf sworn to protect her pack. In Jared's Wolf, two enemies must join forces to stop a killer while learning that love defies all boundaries--even those between species.\n
book.author: MaryJanice Davidson
